                  --Chapter 4: Abduction at Mars-- 


Mars


*Items in Mars:

Sour Syrup, Purple Mist, Silense Card, Silk Robe



*Pickpocket Data:

Robe, 120 Fol, 200 Fol, Ring of Sorrow, Boots, Fairy Glass, Ruby Wand, 

