Linga

@{jcenter} When first getting to Linga, I suggest doing a PA. This action
will allow you to get @{" Precis " LINK "extras/precis.ilbm/MAIN"} and
keep you from getting Bowman, who (IMHO) is not as good a fighter as Prcis.


@{jleft}*Pickpocket Data:



200 Fol, Book of Renki, Counterattack Book, Spice Cake, Kokumotsu, Pet Food, 



Mannenpitsu, Attack Vile, Iron, 1500 Fol, Promise Ring, Artemis Leaf, 300 Fol, 



